OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FOfsted sorry for its role  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fin Ruth Perry's suicide    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ofsted has apologised fully for the    
OL,6, first time for the role it played in   
OL,7, Ruth Perry's suicide and promised a    
OL,8, review of lessons to be learned.       
OL,10,FThe head teacher killed herself while  
OL,11,Fwaiting for an inspection report, in   
OL,12,FJanuary 2023.                          
OL,14,FAfter December's inquest, coroner Heidi
OL,15,FConnor warned of a risk of further     
OL,16,Fdeaths "unless action is taken".       
OL,18,FResponding to her report, on Friday,   
OL,19,FOfsted also promised a major review of 
OL,20,Fhow it handled safeguarding concerns.  
